# Generate the demo GIF:  brew install vhs  &&  vhs demo.tape   (outputs demo.gif)
# For best results, run `receipt import claude-code` in a real project first so `receipt show` has data.
Output demo.gif
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1100
Set Height 680
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 45ms
Type "receipt show"
Enter
Sleep 4s
Type "receipt pr"
Enter
Sleep 5s
